<h2 style="color: #2a3d66; font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 25px; text-align: center;">
  ¡Gracias por tu compra, {{customerName}}!
</h2>

<p style="font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: #4a5568; line-height: 1.6; text-align: center;">
  Te enviamos la boleta de tu curso adquirido:
</p>

<table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: separate; border-spacing: 0 10px; margin-top: 25px; font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; color: #2d3748; background-color: #f7fafc; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);">
  <tr style="background-color: #ffffff;">
    <td style="padding: 15px 25px; border: none; background-color: #ebf4ff; font-weight: 600; color: #2c5282; border-top-left-radius: 10px; border-bottom-left-radius: 10px;">
      Curso:
    </td>
    <td style="padding: 15px 25px; border: none; background-color: #ffffff; color: #4a5568; border-top-right-radius: 10px; border-bottom-right-radius: 10px;">{{courseTitle}}</td>
  </tr>
  <tr style="background-color: #ffffff;">
    <td style="padding: 15px 25px; border: none; background-color: #ebf4ff; font-weight: 600; color: #2c5282; border-top-left-radius: 10px; border-bottom-left-radius: 10px;">
      Monto:
    </td>
    <td style="padding: 15px 25px; border: none; background-color: #ffffff; color: #4a5568; border-top-right-radius: 10px; border-bottom-right-radius: 10px;">
      <strong style="color: #007bff;">{{paymentAmount}} {{currency}}</strong>
    </td>
  </tr>
  <tr style="background-color: #ffffff;">
    <td style="padding: 15px 25px; border: none; background-color: #ebf4ff; font-weight: 600; color: #2c5282; border-top-left-radius: 10px; border-bottom-left-radius: 10px;">
      Inicio del curso:
    </td>
    <td style="padding: 15px 25px; border: none; background-color: #ffffff; color: #4a5568; border-top-right-radius: 10px; border-bottom-right-radius: 10px;">{{startDate}}</td>
  </tr>
  <tr style="background-color: #ffffff;">
    <td style="padding: 15px 25px; border: none; background-color: #ebf4ff; font-weight: 600; color: #2c5282; border-top-left-radius: 10px; border-bottom-left-radius: 10px;">
      ID de orden:
    </td>
    <td style="padding: 15px 25px; border: none; background-color: #ffffff; color: #4a5568; border-top-right-radius: 10px; border-bottom-right-radius: 10px;">
      <span style="background-color: #edf2f7; padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 5px; font-family: 'Consolas', 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 14px; color: #4299e1;">{{orderId}}</span>
    </td>
  </tr>
  <tr style="background-color: #ffffff;">
    <td style="padding: 15px 25px; border: none; background-color: #ebf4ff; font-weight: 600; color: #2c5282; border-top-left-radius: 10px; border-bottom-left-radius: 10px;">
      ID de transacción:
    </td>
    <td style="padding: 15px 25px; border: none; background-color: #ffffff; color: #4a5568; border-top-right-radius: 10px; border-bottom-right-radius: 10px;">
      <span style="background-color: #edf2f7; padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 5px; font-family: 'Consolas', 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 14px; color: #4299e1;">{{transactionId}}</span>
    </td>
  </tr>
  <tr style="background-color: #ffffff;">
    <td style="padding: 15px 25px; border: none; background-color: #ebf4ff; font-weight: 600; color: #2c5282; border-top-left-radius: 10px; border-bottom-left-radius: 10px;">
      Fecha y hora:
    </td>
    <td style="padding: 15px 25px; border: none; background-color: #ffffff; color: #4a5568; border-top-right-radius: 10px; border-bottom-right-radius: 10px;">{{captureTime}}</td>
  </tr>
</table>

<p style="margin-top: 35px; font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: #4a5568; line-height: 1.6; text-align: center;">
  Si tenés alguna consulta, no dudes en escribirnos.
</p>

<p style="font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: #4a5568; line-height: 1.6; text-align: center;">
  Saludos,<br/>
  El equipo de BaraCreativa
</p>

<hr style="border: none; border-top: 2px solid #cbd5e0; margin: 40px auto; width: 60%; max-width: 400px;" />

